# Asset Repository Guidelines

This directory stores all non-code assets for the OceanLabz AI Explorer S3 Board repository.

## Structure

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `images/` | Product photos, screenshots, example output images |
| `datasheets/` | Component datasheets (INMP441, MAX98357A, ESP32-S3, etc.) |
| `diagrams/` | Pinout diagrams, block diagrams, wiring schematics |
| `logos/` | OceanLabz branding assets (SVG, PNG) |
| `3d_models/` | STL/STEP files for 3D-printable enclosures |
| `wiring_guides/` | Fritzing-style wiring illustrations |

## Naming Convention

Follow the conventions defined in [`docs/contributing/documentation-standards.md`](../docs/contributing/documentation-standards.md).

```
[category]_[subject]_[description].[ext]
```

## File Guidelines

- **Images:** PNG or JPG, max 1200 px wide, max 500 KB per image
- **Datasheets:** PDF only, include the manufacturer part number in the filename
- **Diagrams:** SVG preferred (scalable), PNG acceptable for complex renders
- **3D Models:** STL for printable models, STEP for source CAD

## License

All assets in this repository are covered by the same [MIT License](../LICENSE) unless otherwise noted in a subdirectory's own `LICENSE` file. Datasheets remain the property of their respective manufacturers.

> For questions about contributing assets, see [`docs/contributing/CONTRIBUTING.md`](../docs/contributing/CONTRIBUTING.md).
